values:
I know what you're doing, I see it all too clear
I only taste the saline when I kiss away your tears
You really had me going, wishing on a star
But the black holes that surround you are heavier by far
I believed in your confusion, you were so completely torn
It must have been that yesterday was the day that I was born
There's not much to examine, there's nothing left to hide
You really can't be serious if you have to ask me why
I say goodbye...

'Cause I am barely breathing
And I can't find the air
Don't know who I'm kidding
Imagining you care
And I could stand here waiting
A fool for another day
I don't suppose it's worth the price, worth the price
The price that I would pay

Everyone keeps asking, what's it all about?
I used to be so certain and I can't figure out
What is this attraction? I only feel the pain
There's nothing left to reason and only you to blame
Will it ever change?

'Cause I am barely breathing
And I can't find the air
Don't know who I'm kidding
Imagining you care
And I could stand here waiting
A fool for another day
I don't suppose it's worth the price, it's worth the price
The price that I would pay

But I'm thinking it over anyway, I'm thinking it over anyway

I've come to find, I may never know
Your changing mind, is it friend or foe?

I rise above, or sink below
With every time, you come and go
Please don't come and go

'Cause I am barely breathing
And I can't find the air
Don't know who I'm kidding
Imagining you care
And I could stand here waiting
A fool for another day
But I don't suppose it's worth the price, it's worth the price
The price that I would pay

But I'm thinking it over anyway...I'm thinking it over anyway

Well, I know what you're doing...I see it all too clear.........

I know this might sound weird, but i have never wanted someone I could not have. I mean I have liked one person or another, but it was not like I could not have had them if I had pushed the situation. But I have never liked someone and know that I can not be with them even if I pursued it. I feel so strange and dumb about this. 
That is all
I've given up on love, for the time being

I would like and watch Doctor Who more if he was attractive. 
I also like love stories, but my love life has never really been one of happy endings.  I have been disappointed many times, but mostly because I have tried this relationship with the same person.  Which equals to the same out come, no matter how many times you squeeze a lemon you will always get lemon juice.
Definition of a fool: doing the same process multiple times and expecting different results.

.......
Hot summer nights mid July
When you and I were forever wild
The crazy days, the city lights
The way you'd play with me like a child

Will you still love me when I'm no longer young and beautiful
Will you still love me when I got nothing but my aching soul
I know you will, I know you will
I know that you will
Will you still love me when I'm no longer beautiful

I've seen the world, lit it up as my stage now
Channeling angels in, the new age now
Hot summer days, rock and roll
The way you'd play for me at your show
And all the ways I got to know
Your pretty face and electric soul

Will you still love me when I'm no longer young and beautiful
Will you still love me when I got nothing but my aching soul
I know you will, I know you will
I know that you will
Will you still love me when I'm no longer beautiful

....

Oh that grace, oh that body
Oh that face makes me wanna party
He's my sun, he makes me shine like diamonds

Will you still love me when I'm no longer young and beautiful
Will you still love me when I got nothing but my aching soul
I know you will, I know you will
I know that you will
Will you still love me when I'm no longer beautiful
Will you still love me when I'm no longer beautiful
Will you still love me when I'm not young and beautiful

Been watch a bit of Doctor Who, its not bad but I still trying to figure out if I like it.  Six/seven episodes in and I still not sure, its watchable I guess.  
So I am one year older, my life, its is strange.
If all goes well I should be in Italy in the fall, and I am also in 12,000 in debt.  Yeah that sucks.  
So I am still not with Angel.  I have not stopped loving him so that puts me in bind since he still wants to be with me.  It has been about five months since we broke up and the fact that he still wants to work things out impresses me.  But then again, he is still the douche that told me that he is going to get better with or without me, and that he was not going to wait forever.  
Ass.
Believe me I want him to continue seeking therapy, it was in such a lousy state when I was with him.  I don't know what is wrong with him.  Don't think I ever will find out what was wrong. 
He asked me if we could try to work things out earlier this month, I didn't want to. I don't know if that would be a good idea, I told him I still need more time to think about it.  The truth is that I need more time to repair all the damage he cause and it going to take some time.  He is not going to get better over night and I don't think I can handle him doing this to me again.  
I really don't want to go through all this shit with him again. There is no benefit as far as I can see.   
He can't promise me that things will get better, and he decimated all the hope I used to have for us together.  I am just so destroyed.  Can't he see that there is not much left.  
I am not young anymore. I don't want to go through all this bullshit for nothing. I am just so tried. I don't want to do this anymore.
I love him, but I need more time away from him. I need to fix me. 
I am so broken and he doesn't understand. He probability things I am being unfair.  
I don't think he really cares how his actions made me feel for the past two years. I don't want to go back to that. 
If it means giving up on the one person I have love for the last twelve years, then so be it.  
I am tried Angel, I don't have the heart to keep doing this to myself. 
If you really want me, you'll wait for as long as it takes.  It may even take a year.  If you don't want to wait. Then I don't mean that much to you in the first place.  In the end, you will be saving us both a lot of pain.  
If I am not worth waiting for, then you got the wrong girl.  

Me that one chick.

I have been watching romantic films again, which is something that I am sure is not good for me right now.  Fashion and I are on speaking terms now after almost two years of not speaking to each other.  
I am a little unstable right now. I am not quite sure what to do with myself right now.  What has just donned on me is that this whole time I have stressed how Angel is no good for me, well I just figured out that the same can be true of me.  That is to say that I am no good for Angel either.  It took him years to get me to trust him and now since he dashed well,  it would take more years to fix this.  Angel has shown that he is a unstable partner and who wants to have a child with someone like that.  I was not found of the idea oh having children and it is even worse now.  If we got back together like how he would want to, the whole child thing would be up in the air.  He also finds me lazy, and unreliable, which by the way sucks.  I am not what he wants, I am my own person with my own wants and dreams which do not include children. 
We both have very negative opinions of each other, what happen to loving someone for who they are? Well, that is very hard to do sometimes.  
I don't want to marry Angel. It would be a mistake on both ends.  He was right to doubt us, and I should have ended it sooner.  Do not live in fear of getting hurt again, because you will get hurt again. Everyone does not have a perfect somebody for them. It was naive of me to think that way. People are ugly stupid creatures, everyone is ugly inside. 
One has to be a little bit crazy to be happy in this world, lucky for me, that is exactly what I am. 
I dream of a love that is worth the pain.  A love where the good times out weigh the bad.  A love in which I do not have to spend the bulk of it wondering "is it me?"  I am not perfect, no one is.  It is not as if I expect it, I just thought that being decent was something that was not that hard to be.  People however have a wonderful way of disappointing me.  
I am stubborn, childish, overweight, bitchy, lazy, fiery temper when I allow myself to come to a boil, dependent on others, and lacking in ambition. 
I am giving to a fault, loving to a fault, enabling to a fault, devoted to a fault, and can be docile to a fault.  
28 years and my life is just beginning, it may not impress Angel, but it doesn't need to.  
Going to dance with myself

Why has loving you always caused me so much pain? You say that you love me, but could not bear being with me.  You say you want to marry me, but dislike my things in your home. You tell me that you miss me, but in the end you wouldn't let me touch you.  How much rejection and pain you have cause, do you not think I have suffered enough? You are alone, you do not wish to trust your family and your friends have always been shit.  They never really cared about you, I knew this for a long time.  Those people whom only wanted used you, those are the people you choose over me.  Now you see that they don't care and you are lost, but still stay with them.  You choose shit instead of love, you deserve them. We could have been a family, you ruined everything. How dare you come to me, you think just with a sorry, it would fix everything.  You say 'I said I was sorry, now get over it, its no big deal.'  Oh yes, the one who causes the pain is so keen on forgetting and moving on.  But what about me? Do my feelings mean so little to you that all the years of hurt should just be over looked with an "I'm sorry."  I want to hate you, but I find that so hard to do even now.  I loved you so much, and love you still but you are not worthy of being loved by me.  It may take me years but I will move on with my life.  I so wanted to make a home with you, but you ruined it! I suffer because you are an uncaring asshole! I was there for you, and you pushed me away.  I was foolish to believe that someone who could not even make himself happy could bring any joy to another. If all goes well I will be gone in six months, and if I learn to live on my own, I will leave.  I will move out of your reach, and hope never to see you again.  I have been too kind to you, you know this.  You are a liar, a coward, a manipulator, insensitive SOB. 

May you get everything you deserve

No chocolate covered strawberries.  No amount of words can express my disappointment. There was a 90% chance that I was not going to get any, but still had the 10% of hope that I would.  No Christmas present or strawberries, men suck! I hope you day turns out shitty! No, I don't mean that, just uneventful.  (Angel) As for everyone else, I hope you had a great week and have a better weekend! I know I will :D

It has gotten to the point where I am thinking about the good times and not all the reasons as to why I broke up with Angel in the first place.  Mommydearest tells me that this will pass and then I will feel nothing. My cousin whom was cheated on believes that Angel was cheating on me, I told her I have no proof of this.  She asked me what I believe and I said that I don't think so, but hell I could be wrong.  It's not like he was incapable of doing it, he is a selfish and stupid kind of guy.  From what my cousin has been telling me, Angel sure as hell sounds like he was cheating on me.  I had asked if he had/was after the break up but he insisted that he had been faithful to me.  My answer at the time was "I don't except you to be honest about this ever." He wanted to continue the relationship with me so I doubt that he would confess such a thing at that moment.  If he was it would sure as hell make this getting over him a lot easier.  But all I have gotten from him since we broke up is that he misses me and wants to make amends for the pain that he caused.  Yes nice sentiments, you know when they could have been useful, six months ago.  Better yet, a year ago when I asked you to get counseling, or how about after making me cry, again, and again, and again for all those months.  Mommydearest tells me that he did not realize my value till I was gone.  How about he didn't realize my value after he found out that none of his friends gave a shit about him.  Oh that I was the only one that kept putting up with his shit and loved him even after he was so distant with me.   He ruined us by behaving like an asshole.  I have given him too many chances and way too much of my time, I can not do this anymore.  I have to move on.  I can't be stupid anymore hoping that he will be better next time around.  If he really cared about me and my feeling, our relationship, he would have gotten help a long time ago.  Not just wait till I leave him.  I love Angel so much, but he is just a bad person for me.  He is no good, and that will never change because it has not in the twelve years that I have known him.  Every time he has come back, that I have let him back into my life, there are promises that it won't be like the last time.  It may have been four/five years but god how he likes to fuck things up with me.  
You have had you last chance with me Angle.
You ruined it, get better for yourself.  Hopefully you don't fuck over your next relationship the way you did with ours.  
My answer is no, and it is going to stay 'NO'
You had countless of chances with me, and you manage to fuck up each and everyone of them.  You are going to have to live with the consequences of your actions. 
May you be happy one day, as I hope to one day be.

Should have been doing my homework

I miss my Teddy :(
I am going to be alone on Valentines day for the first time in four years. I know that it is weeks away but my little sister thought to mention it to me this weekend.  
I miss him, but it will go away.  It is not as bad as it was when I first ended it in November.  Time will pass and both of us will move on.  It is just sad, I wanted to married this man, he put me through so much and it was he who was not sure about us.  Now I am twenty-eight and alone.  From the look of things I may not find another partner till my early thirties, and if I do get married it won't be till I am in my late thirties early forties.
I am the end of my line.

What a fool I was, what dominated fool To think that you were the Earth and sky What a fool I was, what an elevated fool What a mutton-headed dote was I No, my reverberating friend You are not a beginning and the end There'll be spring every year without you England still will be here without you There'll be fruit on the tree And a shore by the sea There'll be crumpets and tea without you Art and music will thrive without you ..... And there still will be rain on that plain down in Spain Even that will remain without you, I can do without you You, dear friend, who taught so well You can go to (Hell) They can still rule the land without you Windsor Castle will stand without you And without much ado we can All muddle through without you Without you pulling it the tide comes in Without your twirling it, the Earth can spin Without your pushing them, the clouds roll by If they can do without you, ducky, so can I I shall not feel alone without you I can stand on my own without you So go back in your shell I can do bloody well without (you)! MY FAIR LADY - WITHOUT YOU Edited to fit my needs lol

I have been watching Under the Tuscan Sun more often lately, this can't be good sign.  
"You will get over this, you will, one day you will be happy again." 
I have a cold right now, feel tried and lonely and then again I want to be alone.  I don't want to keep pretending to be happy/okay.  I just miss him so much, I know I had every reason to end it with him, but that still does not stop me from missing him. 
What do you do when the person you thought you were going to marry tells you that he doesn't want to.  I yearn for him, but he just didn't want me.  I don't like rejection, and this is the worse kind.  He tells me that he loves me and he will never love anyone as much as he does me.  Oh yeah that I deserve better, that I was really good to him, that he loves and misses me so much, then why after all of this was he still not sure.  I don't understand.  I did nothing wrong.  I was so giving. 
"What is it about love that makes us so stupid?...Why can't [you] just let it go?"
I want to be happy.

Life just sucks sometimes
My sister is wreak
My other sister is not leaving the nest
I dumped my boyfriend after things weren't working out for a few months, then he tells me he was thinking about marrying.  Apparently he got scared and I have to deal with the fact that my boyfriend of four years could not see himself working out with me long term.  Oh but he says that he will always love me.  Great! What am I supposed to do with that information? 
This and finals
I am just so tried, I have not had enough sleep for a while now, I am sad and lonely every now and then.  It erks me to have to think about how one day I will have to start all over again with someone new.  This is bullshit.
I have my whole life ahead of me, but right now I am not feeling so good.
I have so much to look forward to next year, I graduate and if all goes well I will be living in Italy for about four to five months.  
I have so much to look forward to, but really, right now, I feel really low.  I am so sad sometimes.  
Everyone I know has problems that seem a lot worse then mine. (okay maybe one of them is just young) I just have to hold it in all the time.  No one ever really lets me cry it out, they don't want to see me bawling, but what if a good cry is all I need? Just sit there and pat my head and stay hey "I know it hurts, its alright, let it go, you are going to be okay" 
I am pissed, sad, lonely, tried and I get paid very little so I can't even buy myself stuff to make me feel good.  Like really expensive chocolates, sweet wines, movies, fancy clothing, you know shit I really don't need.  
The only way I cheer myself up is making other people smile.  I make jokes (they are not good ones) I act silly, bring candy and cookies to work.  I fine it easier to spend on others than myself. 
Just really over it, not this year, but just how I am.  
Winter is Coming
I broke up with Angel again

I've never had high expectations of myself, so I am not one to say "look at how I wasted my life." I have not done much, but I have done more than what most of my family would have deemed possible for someone like me.  I am a success because of my family deemed me incompetent.  Kinda of sad really.  

I find myself in place surrounded by drowning people, and I have just only learned how to swim
I want to stop and save them, but I know they will only drag me down with them
It is hard for me to leave them there, there are some whom I really wish I could save
But I must keep swimming, I don't know where I am going, only that I must keep moving
I venture out in to the unknown, unsure of myself, it is a vast ocean
Only time will tell whether or not I find land or drown

I am 28 years old and my life feels like it is just starting.  I am moving into adulthood, college is coming to an end, and my time in limbo is almost up.  
I am scared, I have never really done anything on my own, now I am looking at studying in another country for six months, and moving to another state for a masters.  I am opening up myself to new experiences and poverty.

Live your life, regret nothing!

I sometimes wonder if I choosing the right career, the right profession. 
*my thoughts earlier were more clear I just wanted to rewrite thoughts I just had*
God that sounds bad.  Can't even write a sentence correctly.  My brain is fried.  
Well since I really can't remember what it was I was thinking word for word, and damn it, it was a lot more intelligent sounding than this post, I am going start fresh.  
So like I was saying, there reason I am questing my current major choice is because I find that I am inadequate. I find that I don't think like my fellow peers, my writing and thinking process seems to always fall short.  I really don't know what to do with myself as of late.  No, my feeling about art and it's history has not changed, I just find myself falling behind because I don't care to question convention.  My peers are brimming with questions and research topics, I am just happy to learn about the works.  A speaker today stated at a true art historian always has questions.  I am at the stage where I only want answers.  
I once told one of my teachers, that I am blank book, I continue to go to school to attain knowledge.  It has past that point for most of my peers, most of them are graduates, I am just learning the methodologies that come with the field.  I just feel so frustrated with myself at this point.  As if I am not learning fast enough.  
It is like a voice inside myself saying "I know I can be great, just provide me with the information/knowledge to get there."  
Am I just not getting it?
I find that I do not read in to things as much as my peers, whom see complex theories where I only see an argument.  I see a image I get; lines, colors, movement, emotion; my peers get; the struggle of black artists in Latin American culture.  
The fact of the matter is, I just don't see it.  
I don't think that way and it frustrates the hell out of me!
I don't get modern/contemporaneity art.
I see new works, and I might find them nice to look at, get the concept behind the work, but still do not consider/see why it is seen as art.
I am so pissed off right now
If I can't see it as art, what am I doing here?
What is the point of working for a museum where I care nothing for the work it holds?
I am so pissed off right now
With myself and with these works, and this stupid, uncomfortable desk! 
It hurts my arms working on this thing!
It is not enough that I show of for class, do all the assignments, and pass the course, I will never succeed this way.  
I must stand out, right I do, but not in a positive way.  I must be better than my peers, my thinking has to surpassed theirs.  These are my competition in this field and I am still all over the place.  I do not have organized thoughts, I am all emotion and no thought.  
Why don't I get it? 
Why do I hate it?
I love my classes, learning is amazing! Just that every teacher asks for my writing each week, and each week I fall short.   
Passable, forgettable that is all I am right now. 
Hard working, but a ditz.
Would write more but this table is really hurting my elbows and its really pissing me off! 
Fuck y'all!

The Russian promised me that he would seek out therapy this month.  His unhappiness is holding our relationship back.  This journal is to mark the day he said that he would do it.  
That is all I want to talk about for the moment.

I find myself talking a lot about myself (likes, thoughts, random stuff) these days.  I really dislike it, but I am having a hard time controlling myself when it happens.  It's like my brain is set on "ME" and sometimes even I get annoyed with my lacking of giving a shit about other people's opinions/thoughts.  I've caught myself doing this a few times, I don't know what has triggered this "Me" fest.  I feel really stupid for doing this.  I want to stop but I just word vomit all over the place sometimes.  I got to tell myself to shut up when I am with others, or someone might just have the guts to do that for me.  That would be really embarrassing, especially because I think I would deserve it. 
This is my journal so here is does not count.  Who in the hell have I been hanging out with that had me think it's okay to ignore what a person just said and talk about myself?
That is a really bad habit I am getting in to.  
Quick news
Still with Angel
Cat is still alive
Still talking to Spanish Bible 
Going to a 4 year college and working on my BA in AH
Still not speaking to Fashion
Still getting pissed off at myself for not being a better person
Still hoping to better myself in time.

So ends this rant

I feel like I am drowning in my relationship.  I am to a point where I don't know what is keeping me here.  He tells me that he is crazy about me but does not feel like seeing me every week.  He is here now only because he said he would be, not because he wants to.  He is asleep and I have been stuck at my house all weekend.  He tells me that he does not feel like doing anything.  He usually feels that way, I spend my time with him laying around while he sleeps.  I like going out, park, or just to walk around on a nice day.  
I love him but I feel used when we are together. 
It has always been a question of time, how long am I going to put up with him.  How long will I stay this time. 
He makes me want to be a drinker.
I want to drown out my broken heart with a bottle. 
I am in love, but not happy. 
I do not think my current lover has what I need to be happy.
I hate waiting
I am so pissed off at Angel...going to play some warcraft to get my mind off of it.  If he doesn't fix this the way I told him to, there will be no living with me.

Angel wants me to write something nice about him.  
I'll just tell you what I really don't mind sometimes. The farting in his sleep I really don't mind...unless it the smelly kind LOL! His childish behavior can be cute sometimes. We are both really stubborn and it works against us most of the time. He makes me laugh at times, and when he's not being an ass gives in to me. 
When he's in a good mood he lets me walk all over him, which I know is for me to do, but I do it anyway. I can make near unreasonable demands and he'll treat me. He is still in debt Partly because he spending on me. Although i do think he gets confused between I want more; sometimes a kiss and hug mean ten times more than a expensive gift. 
I don't what else to say right now.

<![endif]-->  <p class="MsoNormal">I wanted to write something. He drinks too much, doesn’t think before saying things, farts in his sleep, is quick to get on the defensive, childish, stubborn, irritating, loud, offensive, selfish, inconsiderate, intensive, and he doesn’t get me at all.</p>  <p class="MsoNormal">I went to a wedding last Saturday, while there all of his bad traits began to show.<span style="">  </span>As I sat there and watched him I asked myself if I could really marry this man.<span style="">  </span>It was a no. What do you do with a friend who is completely contradictory?

Worse! She knows that she contradicts herself but when you point it out she flat out denies it!  Then, your boyfriend keeps telling you not to lecture her because that that will only push her away? Why should I censor myself when she gets all uppity?   She does things that she knows; I know she knows it will just end badly.  But she does them anyway, I point that out, she gets upset because she knows that she put herself in that situation.  She asks how anyone can prepare for a relationship, because she believes there is nothing once can do to prepare, I tell her that a person must like themselves to before they can get in to a relationship.  She says that she has never had anyone to grow with…GROWING HAPPENS ON YOUR OWN! YOU CAN NOT EXPECT ANYONE TO COME ALONG TO FIX YOU! IF YOU DON’T LIKE YOURSELF, IT WILL SHOW IN YOUR ATTEMPTS!  Relationships do not turn out well if one, or both of the people in them dislike themselves.  I want her to realize that she has a lot of work to do on herself before she can even start thinking about getting into a relationship. There are going to be MANY things that you don’t like about yourself that you cannot really change.  Self perception is NOT one of them.  Your face, shape (unless you are willing to put in the time and effort to work on it), what you find funny, are some of the things that you are going to have to deal with for the rest of your life. And you will only look worse with age, so if you have a problem with your looks now, it’s not that you are fucked as so much as you have to get over it.  Accept who you are and what you look like NOW, because you will never look this cute again! You will look back on these years and realize how much of an idiot you were to have had a problem with your looks. 

My friend says she thinks she’s hot.  Then she points out men that she believes would never go after her.  I know she thinks that she is prettier than a lot of girls BUT she also puts too much in looks that she is not to happy with.  Meaning, “I would be so much prettier than that girl/or I would so be able to get that guy if I was (thinner, had straight teeth, if I didn’t have these horrible acne marks). When I was younger I didn’t like this, I could get any guy I wanted.”  Can you see the problem with is kind of thinking? Has she actually said any of these things out loud…half of them.  Does she have a point? Well let’s go down the list shall we…

1)       Hot but not hot? You believe both, which I do not understand.

2)      Thin vs Fat: You are not a stick this is true, but if you really had a problem with your weight you have done something about it. Even now you can start running if you really wanted to.

3)      Teeth. There is nothing you can afford to do right now about your teeth, and really they are not that bad.  I don’t think anyone who really wants to get to know you will care about your teeth.

4)      Acne Marks.  You can’t really see them.  If a guy does not want to be with you because of them, there is nothing wrong with you.  The guy is just an ass hoe and who does not deserve YOUR TIME.

5)      When you WERE younger. This has passed, it’s as useful as me saying “When I was 5 I was so small.” There is no point in bring up the past like this.  IT DOES NOT HELP YOU AT ALL.  What is the point in bringing this up? You are not 50, now is not the time to be talking that way.  You are young now! And you are cute now!

This is what is wrong with you! Not your looks! The way you think about yourself is what fucks you over!  Only when you have doubts about yourself do you get upset. I have found this true about you in about any field of conversation we enter. We talk, I unknowingly hit a nerve and you blow things out of proportion. Do I really have to walk on eggshells with you?  I don’t think I can do that.   You ask not be judge, but you are unwilling to accept the faults in those that are closest to you.   How do you think that it feels that we can’t be honest with you because we want to keep you?  You are a smart girl but you are a walking contradiction.
